long_description: we are your partner for your next generation of electrical motors. our brand backpaketiersystem – bps unites our «high speed» bonding technologies. we do tig, plasma and laser welding. our services start in the development phase of your motor. our customers value our know-how, innovations and flexibility.
business_tags: process capabilities | welding | laser welding | aerospace | web services | materials selection | tracks & recordings | electric motors | medtech
generated_description: swd ag stator- und rotortechnik is a technology company that specializes in the development of lamination stacks for axial flow motors. they offer innovative solutions for the next generation of electrical motors and are passionate about achieving optimal weld seams for their lamination stack. their services start from the development phase of the motor and include segmentation of designs to single tooth or segments with several notches, which reduces material usage heavily and allows independent material selection for the rotor. they also offer tig, plasma, and laser welding services. their brand backpaketiersystem® – bps unites their "high speed" bonding technologies, making design feasible where other stacking technologies are not possible. swd ag is a partner for their clients' next generation electrical motors.
generated_business_tags: lamination stacks for motors | high precision stacks | tig and plasma welding process techniques | re-designing electrical sheet stacks
